title: Jieming You
text:
Latest projects


Sähkö Nyt
Electricity price monitoring app for IOS developed entirely using Swift and SwiftUI. Launching early 2023.


Sanajahti Solver
Depth-first search algorithm implementation using Python for solving Sanajahti-game. Web-app built using Flask.


Linear Gaussian Model on Global Warming
Using hierarchical Bayesian model to assess the global warming trend. Using R and Stan for the HMC simulation.


Kernel Convolution study
Using simple kernel convolutions to apply e.g., Gaussian Blur on images. Implemented using base R.
